ADDED FEATURES:
 Expiring in n days mailling generator
 import-stdb utility
 OperServ GETFOUNDER
 SecureNetwork mode option
 VLINE list management
 Real time news delivering (NewsServ)
 Drop Delay
 Multi Root support
 ChanServ ACESS list who changed info
 /ChanServ KICK 
 Smart Language Selection System
 /NickServ JOIN  
 /NickServ SET AUTOX for auto use mode +x
 Customization on setup.h
 NickServ/ChanServ STATS (of the day)
 BOTLIST for wise clone kill protection utilization
 New datafile version scheme (per database)
 Date rotated filenames for logs
 NickServ AJOIN List *
 /NickServ SET AUTOJOIN ON/OFF 
 /NickServ GHOST (RELEASE when needed) command auto identify for nick
 NickServ PROTECTION with nick change to _nick-
 Memo read acknowledge 
 ChanServ PROTECT level 
 OperServ restricted opers control
 Services log to channel #Services.log
 Encrypted passwords 
 Helper umode managing using #HelpChan opers
 Nick change to _nick- on missing identify
 Clean kill system for BOT's not identifying on nick change
 OperServ ZOMBIE/UNZOMBIE for setting umode (+z) zombie
 Opers will join AdminChan on join

